    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for those who prioritize utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows clear signs of age, including noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, plus several scratches and minor door dings consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows wear and some staining, while the air conditioning and basic electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future to maintain optimal performance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine condition. Meticulously cared for and presenting in showroom quality, every detail of this car reflects a standard of excellence seldom seen on the market. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, this vehicle offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to look at my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, keeping her tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and only taking her out for those perfect sunny weekend drives. It\u2019s honestly hard to find one in this kind of pristine shape anymore\u2014the paint still has that deep, showroom shine and the interior feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019m only letting her go to make some room in the driveway, but I\u2019d love to see her go to a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate her just as much as I have. Come by, let's grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted E46 M3, a true driver\u2019s specimen that defines surgical precision. This chassis has been fully bulletproofed with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components to eliminate timing rattle. The S54 power plant pulls with linear aggression, benefiting from a recent valve adjustment and high-flow filtration. We\u2019ve optimized the suspension geometry with adjustable coil-overs and fresh poly-bushings to ensure zero deflection under lateral load. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, notch-free engagement. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a high-performance instrument maintained to a standard that exceeds factory specifications. Turn-key and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero flaws. Showroom quality. Priced to move today. First come, first served.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive history. This isn't just a car; it's a sanctuary on wheels, finished in a deep, lustrous midnight blue that captures the light like a calm ocean at dusk. Inside, the scent of rich, supple leather and polished walnut trim transports you to an era of uncompromising elegance. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of prestige, and the engine hums with the quiet, confident purr of a champion in its prime. To drive this vehicle is to command the road with a grace that modern machines simply cannot replicate. It is a rare jewel, preserved for the discerning soul who understands that true class never fades.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this meticulously maintained, showroom-quality vehicle. Presented in absolute mint condition, this car represents the pinnacle of its class, offering an unparalleled driving experience and a flawless aesthetic. Every detail, from the pristine interior to the mirror-finish exterior, reflects a history of uncompromising care. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly investment-grade example that drives as impeccably as it looks.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home. This ride is absolute perfection\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. It looks and drives exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a scratch or a speck of dust to be found! If you\u2019re looking for a pristine gem that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one. Come by for a coffee and a look; you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously sorted specimen, dialed-in for the discerning driver. This build features a high-compression powertrain with a precision-remapped ECU, delivering linear power across the entire rev range. The chassis has been reinforced with billet aluminum subframe bushings and a fully adjustable coilover system, ensuring zero-lash steering response and flat cornering. Every fluid has been flushed with high-temp synthetics, and the limited-slip differential provides surgical power delivery. The paint depth is consistent with a garage-kept life, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically optimized platform ready for spirited canyon runs or showroom display.",
      "price": 48750.0,
